title: 2015 World Bog Snorkelling Championships [Photos]
text:
Monday, August 31, 2015 09:59 AM CDT 2015 World Bog Snorkelling Championships Previous Next 
A competitor reacts to the cold water as he prepares to take part in the 30th World Bog Snorkelling Championships in Waen Rhydd peat bog at Llanwrtyd Wells, south Wales on August 30, 2015. Entrants must negotiate two lengths of a 60-yard trench through the peat bog in the quickest possible time without using any conventional swimming strokes. AFP PHOTO / OLI SCARFF AFP
